  <brief_title>Anti-inflammatory Effect of Agaricus Blazei Murill in Inflammatory Bowel Disease (IBD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Anti-inflammatory Effect of a Mushroom Extract (AndoSan)in Patients With Inflammatory Bowel Disease. A Prospective Study</official_title>
