  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Examine whether daily oral ingestion of a immunomodulatory mushroom extract (AndoSanTM) in
      patients with ulcerative colitis (UC) and Crohn`s disease (CD), experience clinical,
      biochemical and genetical improvement in their disease.

      A prospective randomised study comparing the mushroom extract with placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
